# CVM simulation {#cvm-sim}

```{r setup, include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = T, warning = F)
options(scipen = 999)
```


```{r}
# Librer√≠as y Recursos ----------------------------------------------------
source("scripts/recursos.R")


# Funciones ---------------------------------------------------------------
source("scripts/funciones.R")
